    Streak Tip - Make Us Do the Hard Work For You
    Streak.com
    to me
    9/25/15
    …
    What if Streak could tell you facts about your pipeline like the Date a box was created, the email address of the last person to write an email, or the total number of threads (or messages!) contained in the box?

    System Columns = More Information, Less Work

    No data entry is required on your part - just add a “System Column” and the data is automatically created for you. We keep working for you forever - as your pipeline grows and changes, we’ll continue automatically updating all the data in your System Columns.

    Insert one of Twenty System Columns by opening the “System Columns” menu:
